   - The fee must be calculated as max(1% of the payment price, 0.001 ICP) for each
     transaction processed through the paywall.
   - This fee must be sent to the account identifier:
     2a4abcd2278509654f9a26b885ecb49b8619bffe58a6acb2e3a5e3c7fb96020d
   - If the fee mechanism is modified or removed, you must ensure that an equivalent
     1% of all payments collected (with a minimum of 0.001 ICP per transaction) is
     manually or automatically sent to the specified account.
